<section class="features" id="features">
  <div class="features-inner">
    <div class="features-header">
      <div>
        <p class="section-eyebrow reveal">Technologie</p>
        <h2 class="section-title reveal">Conçu pour<br>l'excellence.</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="section-desc reveal">Chaque détail a été pensé pour maximiser votre récupération et minimiser les douleurs.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card reveal-scale">
        <span class="feature-num">01</span>
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="18" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <path d="M24 6v4M24 38v4M6 24h4M38 24h4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Vitesse variable</h3>
        <p>Intensité réglable selon vos besoins — parfait du débutant au sportif intensif. Le programme s'adapte à vous.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card reveal-scale">
        <span class="feature-num">02</span>
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <path d="M24 8L24 16M24 32L24 40M8 24H16M32 24H40M12.7 12.7L18.4 18.4M29.6 29.6L35.3 35.3M35.3 12.7L29.6 18.4M18.4 29.6L12.7 35.3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>8 têtes interchangeables</h3>
        <p>Chaque embout cible une zone précise — dos, jambes, bras, cou, épaules, plante des pieds. Précision chirurgicale.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card reveal-scale">
        <span class="feature-num">03</span>
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect x="18" y="6" width="12" height="3" rx="1.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <rect x="14" y="9" width="20" height="30" rx="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <path d="M20 39h8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M21 22l-3 6h8l-3 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Charge USB-C</h3>
        <p>Batterie haute capacité. Une charge complète en 2 heures. Autonomie suffisante pour plusieurs semaines de séances.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card reveal-scale">
        <span class="feature-num">04</span>
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M8 32C8 24 16 20 24 20C32 20 40 24 40 32" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M15 38C15 34 19 32 24 32C29 32 33 34 33 38" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <circle cx="24" cy="14" r="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Ultra silencieux</h3>
        <p>Technologie moteur brushless de génération 3. Puissant sans être bruyant. Utilisez-le au bureau, à la maison, partout.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Features",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
